data.title: DML: Digital Mathematics Library: Retrodigitized Mathematics Journals
data.text:
DML: Digital Mathematics Library

Retrodigitized Mathematics Journals and Monographs

Retrodigitized and augmented version of page 920 from Allyn Jackson: "The Digital Mathematics Libary",

Notices of the Am. Math. Society, vol. 50, Number 8, 2003 [Local Copy]

For a similar list, compare http://www.wdml.org

The databasis for this table is an ascii-based list, parseable by a small PERL script.

If you want items to be added here, please send me the necessary data.

If you click on "Title" below, you get a list ordered by title, similarly with "Author", "Repository" (sorting by its full name), and "Type". (Sorting by "Author" gives a list only with those items - like books - having an author entry.)
